## Version 8.3.11

- fix map drawing for editable features

## Version 8.3.10

- options to watch QGIS projects for changes and reload them automatically

## Version 8.3.9

- allow editable fields to be empty
- fixed race condition in gdal module

## Version 8.3.8

- fixed CRS transformation issues for certain projections

## Version 8.3.7

- action `qfieldcloud` can now be defined per project
- added `name` option for image formats

## Version 8.3.6

- fixed screenshot export functionality

## Version 8.3.5

- fixed preview URLs for "file" database fields
- invalid CRS transforms are now logged as warnings instead of errors
- fixed client toolbar visibility issue

## Version 8.3.4

- minor bugfixes

## Version 8.3.3

- fixed MapProxy cache issues, added `concurrency` option for cache CLI
- support for LDAP SSL mode
- authorization redirect upon a successful login

## Version 8.3.2

- added support for QField Cloud protocol

## Version 8.3.1

- bugfixes from 8.2.18

## Version 8.3.0

- support for http POST forms
- server startup script now uses a template
- added option `allowInsecureFrom` for secure requests
